        <a href="https://github.com/KreativeThinker" class="inline space-x-2 justify-center text-md"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i><p class="md:inline hidden">KreativeThinker</p></a>
        <a href="https://linedin.com/in/anumeya-sehgal" class="inline space-x-2 justify-center"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i><p class="md:inline hidden">Anumeya Sehgal</p></a>
